WEBVTT

00:00:23.760 --> 00:00:24.560 line:20%
'Kerajaan Angga.'

00:00:24.600 --> 00:00:26.920 line:20%
Saya merasa baik sekarang.
Sangat bagus!

00:00:26.960 --> 00:00:29.120 line:20%
Dan saya ingin
melihat istana sekarang.

00:00:30.240 --> 00:00:31.120 line:20%
Karna.

00:00:31.960 --> 00:00:34.080 line:20%
Ayo, tunjukkan padaku istananya.

00:00:35.880 --> 00:00:36.840 line:20%
Apakah kamu ingat?

